title: Season 6 ending
body:
I was silver 1 and i just finished climbing gold at 1h00 am so does that mean that im 1 hour too late and i won't get the rewards for the season?...
{{item:3070}}  :(

I don't know if u could do something? The other seasons were longer than this one...

thank you :$

replies.body:
It's hard for me to tell exactly what tier you ended the season at until ranked rewards are distributed. For reference, [this post](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/230496748) goes over the eligibility for a match to count if you were playing on with *literal minutes* to spare. 

I'd recommend waiting for us to get all those ranked rewards out and if you have any issues or questions to reach back out.
thank you everything is fine :) love you <3
